Interface Node

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ExceptionHandlingNode<R>, Expression<R>, RebuildableNode<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDeferredExpression, BinaryOperationExpression, BinaryPredicateExpression, BinaryPredicateIterableExpression, ConversionOperationExpression, CreationOperationExpression, DiscreteFunctionToIterableExpression, DoubleScript, FunctionalExpression, IterableExpressionToIterable, IterableOperationExpression, PickExpression, ResolvedExpression, TensoricScript, UnaryOperationExpression

    public interface Node
    A marker interface for any node in the instruction tree, which later will be processed by a tree walker.
